                                        },
                                        {
                                            "name":  "Wil-O-Wisp",
                                            "description":  "Cast forward a spectral image of Wisp to confuse and distract enemies. Reactivate to travel to its position. Hold to have the image travel faster and teleport to its position on release. ",
