                                            "imageName":  "WispLight.png"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "name":  "Breach Surge",
                                            "description":  "Open a dimensional breach to overwhelm nearby enemies and cause them to release aggressive Surge sparks when damaged.\nWisp may also target a Reservoir to teleport to it and double the range of the surge.",
